METADATA.keywords: Chinese Communist Party, China, assests, Hong Kong, real estate, Xi Jinping, Li Qianxin, national security law
METADATA.description: Hong Kong, August 13 (ANI): The three top leaders of Chinese Communist Party including President Xi Jinping, have relatives who own assets in Hong Kong, an investigation by the New York Times revealed.
